        "instructionText": "Beat the whole egg + egg white with the brown sugar only until the sugar grit dissolves and it looks smooth and glossy — then STOP. This builds chew and the shiny top; do NOT whip it to a pale, voluminous ribbon, which aerates it and bakes up holey/cakey."
      }
